 and denominator d sub i, end sub, plus d sub o, end fraction. \"><math alttext=\"the fraction with numerator d sub i, end sub, times d sub o, and denominator d sub i, end sub, plus d sub o, end fraction. \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>o</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>o</mi></msub></mrow></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">D</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Inverted</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction with numerator d sub i, end sub, times d sub o, and denominator the absolute value of d sub i, end sub, minus d sub o, end absolute value, end fraction. \"><math alttext=\"the fraction with numerator d sub i, end sub, times d sub o, and denominator the absolute value of d sub i, end sub, minus d sub o, end absolute value, end fraction. \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>o</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><mo>|</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>o</mi></msub><mo>|</mo></mrow></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n","rubricRef":"VR857481_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">A</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">B</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">C</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">D</p>"],"answer":1}]